{"tid":472220,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦成日用用下自動熄機","createTime":"2017-11-18T04:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T00:32:17.000Z","uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"15a1053db16400cfc96e4aa1a7fab0d329f096d3","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:27:56.000Z","msg":"部腦近期成日用用下自動熄機，之後唔可以即時開機，要等一段時間之後先至可以開到機，或者要拔掉插蘇+底板Power同reset線重新插落去先至可以開機(一時可以一時唔得)。<br />\n我檢查過CPU加番散熱膏，將d Ram拔掉重插，風扇亦正常運作，底板同埋Display卡表面亦正常，冇任何異味，機箱塵都唔係多，唔知乜嘢原因，每次熄機時間都唔一樣，有時登入使用者就熄機，有時聽緊歌一開瀏覽器就熄機，亦可以用緊MS office果陣熄機搞到d工作要重新做過(有時唔記得save)。<br />\n<br />\n完全唔知點解......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1dafa858077a4189257f135611ff7c90dccbcc0","tid":472220,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"死底板/牛<br />\n換過隻牛試下先<br />\n照樣出事就即係死板"},{"pid":"50f5cf026955faf268ca0f9b202104eae138bb96","tid":472220,"uid":21047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:31:25.000Z","msg":"主機電源線壞左 我之前係咁"},{"pid":"ce8b131e696dc053f3a667919d4d64278de1c902","tid":472220,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"似死板多btw"},{"pid":"9e9ced1dbdfb34455af91bb708f125fb3602f406","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"但係現在我開到機 仲可以上網睇YouTube <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92eaefc8fcf73947131c4159d3619738635079d8","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"唔似底板出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877c8ccbcf44f7e2bd2347f3b2add9500f7075f4","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>主機電源線壞左 我之前係咁</blockquote><br />\n我發現機箱reset掣冇反應 其實好耐之前已經係咁 只係我冇理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3345c733453df017301b6453dee58a23b1d482cd","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>主機電源線壞左 我之前係咁</blockquote><br />\n我發現機箱reset掣冇反應 其實好耐之前已經係咁 只係我冇理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係電源線壞，應該點樣搞？係唔係要換新機箱？"},{"pid":"420b155e8da6f43e02d85cfc8cde5f80dbf5383e","tid":472220,"uid":42759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"換火牛啦<br />\n早幾個月都試過 一換火牛即刻冇事"},{"pid":"32c541b9c5cf5358c5a8fb8cc06e5ff4b3629483","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱用左成差唔多2小時都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我懷疑係機箱電源線問題，火牛好似唔係問題主因。"},{"pid":"9731b10d8aea6bdf1798dbbe9808bfe6553b8c7b","tid":472220,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:14:46.000Z","msg":"一打FPS game，同埋3d test會自動重新開機，係咪要換牛<br />\n<br />\n其他情況下，乜事都有正正常常"},{"pid":"863734c1de71b9ab7fd060e476e575afe3c42add","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"shit... 啱啱一開Firefox，即刻熄左機，底板仲有電，但係按Power掣冇反應，又係咁樣...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9053d12d7c1cea2771e5700cd3b8f6fe4a4affd","tid":472220,"uid":104613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"522414648443c0e4a1065aa00ad15f626dfd784c","tid":472220,"uid":73294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"搭單問下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n部DELL 7567 尋日更新完就好撚奇怪<br />\n部機每隔一陣仔就會卡左咁款<br />\n即係連打緊呢段字都係打左幾粒字就跳左出去打唔到 <br />\n要禁返一下左鍵返黎先打得返字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有冇巴打解救到我"},{"pid":"ef69af1cc03f7c8d79ec1389e35f4060fdd043e0","tid":472220,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"3cff6bf32be62d3797d7c8cefc1fda969a14b3ea","tid":472220,"uid":100950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:23:52.000Z","msg":"我之前都係咁 燒火牛"},{"pid":"a387f9d09d8f61c358e63c7e217d64693e1df374","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱用左成差唔多2小時都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我懷疑係機箱電源線問題，火牛好似唔係問題主因。</blockquote><br />\n快D換牛, 下下無啦啦斷電好傷件</blockquote><br />\n我諗緊要唔要換埋機箱，因為機箱電源線都神神地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed4e9026dc40f57bfc8bf2fb47fc09eaa1fb0e8","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:28:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啱啱用左成差唔多2小時都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我懷疑係機箱電源線問題，火牛好似唔係問題主因。</blockquote><br />\n快D換牛, 下下無啦啦斷電好傷件</blockquote><br />\n我諗緊要唔要換埋機箱，因為機箱電源線都神神地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇火牛+機箱推介 <br />\n<br />\n我部老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/142750_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F142750_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3324e9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/142823_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F142823_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5a25b7fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/18/142830_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F18%2F142830_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=185584b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a36c00d7272a08a6e797d6b8bab452d30e0f53b0","tid":472220,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:34:00.000Z","msg":"自己換牛，有咩要留意，唔識砌機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfb116751d3f305ae0bc6de7370a1475989f7b8","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T09:57:51.000Z","msg":"求火牛、機箱推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d49106b2b4523624d584ca0761998cf972a0ff","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求火牛、機箱推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推"},{"pid":"9df53c700bc061648b176d51684f600d27d3adae","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>求火牛、機箱推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推</blockquote><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f8240c3efd50a41c64be544cc2cfcf1e1571d8","tid":472220,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>求火牛、機箱推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\